metadata.name: Tender Touch
metadata.description:
Tender Touch is one of multi-edition artwork from Gentle Hues collection.  
The Gentle Hues art collection is a beautiful selection of pastel-colored artworks created using AI. Featuring soft shades of pink, blue, green, and more, this collection is perfect for adding a touch of calm and tranquillity to any space. From delicate florals to architecture, each piece in the Gentle Hues collection has its own unique charm and personality.
